These are ROOTLESS, systemd --user, and were proven by hand on one VM. Bake in
exactly the following hard-won requirements (do not "simplify" them away):
  - Runs rootless as the `solace` service user via a systemd --user unit;
    linger enabled; container started ONLY by `systemctl --user`, never by
